data.description: Very spacious home that would be a perfect investment for a nice rental or home to live in a central location near everything. This home features 4 bedrooms. The front living room is a very large space perfect for entertaining or family get togethers. The main bath has a whirlpool tub and the shower in the master bath has handrails for an elderly person. Upgraded items over the past few years include carpet, water heater, roof and kitchen countertops and tile backsplash. Even though there are still a few updates that could be made the house has been well maintained over the years and is perfectly livable in its current condition. This is a very good value for the amount of living space. This is an "As Is" price. The property may be able to be financed in its current condition but repairs of any kind, concessions, or closing costs would need to be added to the purchase price.
